BY HEMBADOON ORSAR MAKURDI Suspected fulani terrorists on Saturday attacked the convoy of Benue State Governor, Samuel Ortom. Our Correspodent gathered from Government Official that the incident, happened at Tyo- Mu along Makurdi/Gboko road around midday. It was also gathered that the governor was on his way to Makurdi when the fulani terrorists opened fire on his convoy but were repelled by his security men.